ass="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link yaml_parse()} - Parse a YAML stream</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link yaml_parse_url()} - Parse a Yaml stream from a URL</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link yaml_emit()} - Returns the YAML representation of a value</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.yaml.php">Yaml 函数</a></div></div>
